---
title: Glazed Chicken Gyozas on Sweet Potato Salad with Peanuts and Gochujang Mayo Drizzle
description: Pronounced gee-oh-zuh, you can find these delicious Japanese style dumplings filled with a mixture of minced meat and/or veg, but these ones are stuffed with chicken! Our Glazed Chicken Gyozas on Sweet Potato Salad is paired with peanuts and a punchy gochujang mayo drizzle.
